import React, { Component } from 'react'
import './Main.css'
import Color from './Color'

export default class Main extends Component {
  render() {
    return (

        <main className="container py-4">
      
        {/* new task */}
        <section className="add-newtask d-flex align-items-center">
          
          <input data-taskdivision="daily" type="text" id="newtask-input" className="shadow rounded-pill" placeholder="New Task ..." />
          
          <article className="newtask-colorbox mx-3 d-flex align-items-center">
            <Color bg='bg-purple'></Color>
            <Color bg='bg-primary'></Color>
            <Color bg='bg-info'></Color>
            <Color bg='bg-orange'></Color>
            <Color bg='bg-warning'></Color>
          </article>
          
          <button type="submit" id="newtask-submit" onClick={newTaskS} className="mybtn btn-success inactive-btn">
            Submite
          </button>
        
        </section>
  
        {/* tasks */}
        <section id="task-container" className="taskbox d-flex flex-wrap align-content-start mt-4 p-2 shadow-in rounded-2">
        
        </section>
      
      </main>
      
    )
  }
}
